object.content:
lays down under a tree in the forest with nothing to do and I then see you walking by
((Open rp))

Jessica stumbles and rolls her ankle.
Ouch! Son of a..!
she looks at you and tilts her head

Looks at you..
I rolled my ankle.. Sorry.
You don't have to apologize.... Are you okay?
I rolled my ankle.. But I'll be fine.
I have a friend that lives in the forest in a tent.
Sorry for asking about why you asked then.

So uhm...
You don't mind me asking if we can take a walk together?
She stands and holds out her hand.
she tilts her head ... Are you... Blushing..?
.. Uh... Okay.. lets go of your hand
.. I think there is a river nearby..

Follows behind, looking down.
I wonder how I can make her my friend....
keeps walking .. Hey, are you okay..? You're quiet now....

Looks down more.
Oh... Now she is suspecting...
No.. I am fine.
.. It's not a bad thing to be weird.. Is it?
